name: Eye detail for HKI
description:
This detail of a WIP was minted to be auctioned for charity.  The creator (Pookie) will match (up to $1000) and additionally send %100 of all proceeds to Helen Keller International which combats the causes and consequences of blindness and malnutrition around the world.  This is a world renowned charity co-founded by the great Helen Keller.  See more at https://www.hki.org/

Proof of donation will be forwarded to the auction winner and also posted on twitter https://twitter.com/Pookie_MD_

This is a hand drawn detail of a WIP.
